  ⚠ eslint(use-while): Use `while` instead of `for` with no init and update.
   ╭─[use_while.tsx:1:1]
 1 │ for (; x < 10;) { x++; }
   · ───
   ╰────
  help: Replace `for(;condition;)` with `while(condition)` for clarity.

  ⚠ eslint(use-while): Use `while` instead of `for` with no init and update.
